♪No distraction is allowed♪

920
00:45:13,241 --> 00:45:16,301
♪A touch of love, a trace of hate♪

921
00:45:16,561 --> 00:45:19,071
♪No need to question♪

922
00:45:20,961 --> 00:45:23,941
♪The truth and falsehood♪

923
00:45:23,941 --> 00:45:27,031
♪Needs to be discerned♪

924
00:45:27,791 --> 00:45:31,131
♪Seeking warmth in peril♪

925
