♪Even in a fateful clash♪

932
00:45:53,511 --> 00:45:55,331
♪With eyes stained with blood♪

933
00:45:55,331 --> 00:45:58,581
♪She holds no grudge♪

934
00:45:58,791 --> 00:46:01,151
♪She does not trust fate♪

935
